  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: gist support is gone when implementing validation that forces user to use Pluto to create extensions.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nboth gist and ipfs are allowed as extension providers\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\npluto allows to install extensions from url, but Status doesn't because of this validation function:\r\n\r\n```(defn valid-uri? [s]\r\n  (boolean\r\n   (when s\r\n     (re-matches (re-pattern (str \"^\" uri-prefix \"\\\\w+@\\\\w+\")) (string/trim s)))))```\r\n",
